==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*τρέμω / tremō / trem'-o

===Etymology===
*Strengthened from a primary word τρέω treō (to “dread”, “terrify”)

===Verb===
'''τρέμω'''

# To “tremble” or fear; to be [[afraid]], trembling.

